data.description: Gorgeous 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in popular Rivermont. Set on a tree-filled half acre, this residence offers tons of greenery and privacy. Featuring an open living space with vaulted ceilings in the living room and a stone fireplace. Tons of windows throughout bringing in natural light. Large master suite equipped with a shower, tub, and a walk-in closet. Great sized secondary rooms and dedicated utility room. Enjoy the peaceful yard and the neighborhood access to the Guadalupe River - living the Texas Hill Country lifestyle!
